displayChart.description: Your weekly update of the most popular tracks in Ludhiana, India.

labels.name: Sony Music Entertainment India Pvt. Ltd.

highlights.text: “Schedule” by Tegi Pannu and Manni Sandhu has been on Top Songs Ludhiana the longest, at 55 weeks straight.
Sidhu Moose Wala has the most spots on Top Songs Ludhiana. “The Last Ride” is the highest at #11.
“Jhaanjar (From "Honeymoon")” by B Praak and Jaani is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Ludhiana, up 49 spots at #28.
“6 L” by Tarsem Jassar and Kulbir Jhinjer is the highest new entry on Top Songs Ludhiana at #79.
